('Kochi', '652 10th Avenue, New York NY 10036', 'Manhattan', 'Korean', 'A', 5, 'Per se alum chef Sungchul Shim‚Äôs $145 nine-course tasting of skewers inspired by Korean royal court cuisine. A sool pairing is also available for $105. Kochi first opened in 2019 and was subsequently awarded a Michelin star.', '5:00pm - 9:30pm', 'https://www.kochinyc.com/' ),
('Crown Shy', '70 Pine Street, New York NY 10005', 'Manhattan', 'American', 'A', 3, 'This 2019 opening was longtime chef de cuisine at Michelin-starred Eleven Madison Park James Kent‚Äôs first solo venture. Crown Shy still turns out excellent food and beautiful cocktails in an elegant environment that‚Äôs equal parts special occasion destination and nicer-than-normal evening whim.', '5:30pm - 12:00am', 'https://www.crownshy.nyc/' ),
